.eslintrc*
.prettierrc*
README.md
*.md

# Docker files themselves
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
docker-compose*.yml

# Tests / coverage
__tests__
coverage
*.test.ts
*.test.tsx
*.spec.ts
*.spec.tsx
